<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SILVERMD - Développeur</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Section principale */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: #00ffff;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: #8892b0;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* Carte de profil */
        .profile-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .profile-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00ffff, #ff00ff);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .profile-info h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .profile-info .title {
            color: #00ffff;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .profile-info .description {
            color: #8892b0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        /* Stats */
        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .stat-card .number {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #00ffff;
        }

        .stat-card .label {
            color: #8892b0;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Projets */
        .projects {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .project-card p {
            color: #8892b0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .project-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #00ffff;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Compétences */
        .skills {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .skill {
            background: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #00ffff;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #8892b0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: #8892b0;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #00ffff;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .profile-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .profile-info .description {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>⚡ <span>SILVERMD</span> ⚡</h1>
            <p>Développeur · Créateur du bot SILVERMD</p>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card">
            <div class="profile-header">
                <div class="avatar">
                    🦊
                </div>
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <h2>SILVER</h2>
                    <div class="title">🚀 Développeur full-stack · Bot WhatsApp</div>
                    <div class="description">
                        Passionné par l'automatisation et les nouvelles technologies. 
                        Créateur du bot WhatsApp SILVERMD, je transforme les idées en lignes de code 
                        pour offrir des solutions innovantes et puissantes.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="number">15+</div>
                <div class="label">Commandes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="number">100%</div>
                <div class="label">Disponibilité</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="number">24/7</div>
                <div class="label">Support</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="number">500+</div>
                <div class="label">Utilisateurs</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skills">
            <span class="skill">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="skill">Node.js</span>
            <span class="skill">Baileys</span>
            <span class="skill">Python</span>
            <span class="skill">HTML/CSS</span>
            <span class="skill">MongoDB</span>
            <span class="skill">WhatsApp API</span>
        </div>

        <div class="projects">
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>🦊 SILVERMD BOT</h3>
                <p>Bot WhatsApp puissant avec gestion de groupes, téléchargement de médias, IA intégrée, et bien plus encore.</p>
                <span class="project-tag">WhatsApp Bot</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>⚡ AUTOMATION</h3>
                <p>Outils d'automatisation pour WhatsApp, gestion des groupes, anti-link, anti-promote, système de bienvenue.</p>
                <span class="project-tag">Automation</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>🎵 MULTIMÉDIA</h3>
                <p>Extraction audio, téléchargement YouTube, conversion de stickers, sauvegarde de vues uniques.</p>
                <span class="project-tag">Multimédia</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">GitHub</a>
                <a href="#">Discord</a>
                <a href="#">WhatsApp</a>
                <a href="#">Twitter</a>
            </div>
            <p>© 2026 SILVERMD - Tous droits réservés</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
